{"tid":807312,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"迎接新隊友 簡迪又做怕醜仔","createTime":"2018-09-05T11:50:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-05T12:41:52.000Z","uid":59732,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"35c76f4e38884f7d90cfeb6a6817d6b1d69c939f","tid":807312,"uid":59732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T11:50:30.000Z","msg":"作為防守中場，雖然於球場上經常與其他球員有身體接觸，不過簡迪卻是一名怕醜仔，日前法國國家隊迎接新隊友的晚宴上，有球員於場內高歌，坐在對方身旁的簡迪竟然顯得十分尷尬。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n由於熱刺門將洛里斯受傷，令蒙彼利埃門將利甘迪 ( Benjamin Lecomte ) 首次入選法國國家隊。周二的球隊晚宴中，除了作自我介紹外，這位國家隊新丁更唱歌娛賓，當他拿起酒樽，站在座位上放膽高歌時，在場所有隊友都為他打拍子和歡呼，唯獨坐在利甘迪旁邊的簡迪卻顯得一面尷尬，不但沒有跟隨節拍揮動毛巾，更四處張望，十分害羞。<br />\n<br />\n事實上，作為現今球壇第一防中，簡迪作風低調、為人內斂，今屆世界盃上，貴為法國隊奪得世界盃的功臣之一，賽後他竟然不好意思與獎盃合照，最後要由隊友尼桑斯將獎盃給他才留下倩影。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?time_continue=35&amp;v=LdmB1XJv1ok\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Ftime_continue%3D35%26v%3DLdmB1XJv1ok&d=MWJ%2FoQsH6fUX2op4UrBM2viMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=34cc7e2b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?time_continue=35&amp;v=LdmB1XJv1ok</a>"},{"pid":"8cc2c8460cf9c153aa4f0a34898e8e09a5727288","tid":807312,"uid":57035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T11:52:17.000Z","msg":"有ching話佢上唔到大枱"},{"pid":"f3b783afc726694fc9a9e8b26247d7b6350d7f53","tid":807312,"uid":37757,"like":30,"dislike":1,"score":29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T11:55:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/cFQYT4O.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FcFQYT4O.gif&h=8090b789&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1ec805acdd6b783c048c67f4ceec06ff7b8a2db4","tid":807312,"uid":1426,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T11:55:27.000Z","msg":"佢會唔會比倫敦金呃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc41becde362dce77b2745ce8b453195bc5fe335","tid":807312,"uid":